Poka¿ w zasobniku systemowym
Allows showing currently selected graph values in the icon in system tray area.

Wskazówki:
- You must activate and select desired graph to get access to this option.
- You may hold <Shift> button pressed on your keyboard while changing this option to change it synchronically for all graphs.
- You may select color for tray icon output by clicking the adjacent color preview field.
